                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Power BI desktop comes with a set of Native visuals. In addition to these, custom visuals can be imported. Custom visuals may be certified by Microsoft which means they have undergone a rigorous review process. Certified visuals are recommended over non-certified, however, as these are managed by the vendors and not Microsoft, the level of rigor in relation to the release management process can not be relied upon. For this reason, custom visuals should be used with caution and the accepted risk they may be changed by the vendor (in particular free non-licenced visuals). ",
